|-- product.h
|-- CMakeLists.txt
|-- README.md

Error Handling
- Prevents empty input fields
- Ensures quantity and price are valid numbers
- Displays error messages using QMessageBox

Future Improvements
- Implement a maximum inventory size (capacity limit) to simulate real-world storage constraints and prevent unlimited item additions
- Add a "brand" attribute to each product to allow better categorization and organization
- Save and load inventory data from files
- Add low stock alerts for items with small quantities
- Implement sorting and filtering options
- Add profit and loss tracking

Use of AI Tools
AI tools were used for debugging assistance, understanding Qt, and improving code structure. All code was reviewed and understood before submission.

Conclusion
This project demonstrates the use of object-oriented programming concepts combined with GUI development. It provides a simple and functional system for managing inventory.
